3.0
        * redesign error handling routine.
        * use spl_autoload_register() instead of __autoload().
        * add isAjax() method to WsController class.
        * add redirect() method to WsController class.
        * add sendResponse() methot to WsController class.
        * add currentUser() and currentUserID() methods to
          WsAuth class.
        * add getLang() method to WsLocalize class.
        * code cleanup.
        * bug fixes.

2.3
        * autocreate database tables on first run.
        * add execute_batch methot to WsDatabase class whic executes
          SQL scripts on database.
        * bug fixes.

2.2
        * add WsChart class for chart drawing.
        * bug fixes.

2.1
        * add WsImage class for simple image manipulation.
        * add support for SQLite database engine.
        * bug fixes.

2.0
        * First stable/useful (to someone) version.

